{
  "title": "Xtra Lazy Jamaican Hind Shank Stew",
  "description": "A hearty, mustardy Jamaican hind shank stew perfect for a lazy Sunday, featuring pickle and Mediterranean-friendly flavors.",
  "cuisine": "Jamaican",
